# Contact form (Web3Forms — backend-less, works on static hosting).
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter the inbox that should receive
#    submissions (e.g. hello@curiuz.com).
# 2. Copy the Access Key they email you into the value below.
# 3. Save this file as `.env.local` (without `.example`) and restart the dev server.
# The key is public by design — safe to expose in client-side code.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
